headline.print_headline: No Time for Regrets, Says Spain Defender Ramos
headline.main: No Time for Regrets, Says Spain Defender Ramos

lead_paragraph: Sergio Ramos declared he was not going to spend another second beating himself up over Spain's 5-1 World Cup defeat to the Netherlands but, like Dutch strikers the night before, the questions kept on coming.
